snippet.textDisplay:
Kevain tenu mein dikhaawan

Dillon russ gayi aan chaawaan

Teri yaadan ich bikhra

mein, dunya sajaawaan..

Sunn ve mein kithay jaawaan

Hun chupp gayi aan raawaan

Mei te dassiya si,

khwaabaan ich takya si

Le hun din v nai chariya

te dil ich tu`n

Meray mann ich tu`n

Jaddon vi nai hondi paas

Te tarapdi ay rooh

Te ravein tu kareeb

sohni, haali na tu ja

Tu hi hai mera naseeb

Kaddi vi na jaavein door

Assi laa dittay jinnay

vi tu mangdi ay taaray,

Meri jaan kaddi vi na

darri meray pyaaray

dil ich tu

Meri hasrat ay tu

Assi teray uttay marday

ne, sunday nai kyu..

Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday

Teray husn uttay marday assi roz

Ki kariye sajna bol,

Sajjnaa..

Haan..Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray

Teray pyaar ich kariye ki hun bol

Sajna kya aavan kol..

✦✦✦

Kinnu poochaa mein

Esaas kithay rakhday ne, Gallan

taalday, Te naal kevain, Hassday ne

Chad ditti mei umeedaan saari dunya ton

Aiwein lokaan diyaan

gallan ich phassday ne


Nai Mei ni bol diyaan jhoot,

meray te tera ay suroor

Teray uttay likhan

ganay sonay jachday ne

dilaan dee yaari saadi, ve

dilaan da nayyo ae kasoor

Naal rehna si zaroor,

saaday thay iraaday..

Mera koye hor nai ae dass ditta dunya nu

Jaddon vi aavay apne

naal lavay khushian nu

Jaddon v door javay,

Jaan saadi kadd javay

Sajna ay teray kol vassna e chaavay

Muskura ke lay litti ay saadi zimevaari

Ni mein nai kitti kaddi

vi teray ton badgumaani

Tu mera yaar si, dil aasmaan paar si

Ae dou dillaan da pyaar si o

Pyaar na si kaghazi par..

Meri khaahish ay tu`n

Meri hasrat ay tu`n

Assi teray utthay marday

ne manday nai kyun


Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday

Teray husn uttay marday assi roz

Ki kariye sajna bol.

Sajjnaa..

Haye..Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray

Teray pyaar ich kariye ki

hun bol Sajna kya aavan kol..


✦✦✦

Tere te mein waari jaavaan

Tere gunn gaavaan meinn..ehh..

Tere bin jee lagda nay aeee...

Bus tenu chavaan mein

hun raava morrr..


Hun te roz tenu chaanday jaanday

Teray husn uttay marday assi roz

Ki kariye sajna bol..

Sajjnaa..

Haan..Teray hi jhol uttay nachday saaray

Teray pyaar ich kariye ki hun bol

Sajna kya aavan kol...

snippet.textDisplay: I'm impressed that the MV is inspired by Shakespeare's Othello, where a jealous man Lago used a handkerchief, a gift from Othello to Desdemona, as a key piece of evidence, leading Othello to believe that Desdemona gave it to his lieutenant Cassio, further fueling his jealousy. The concept of red scarf resembles the handkerchief a lot🧣❤️‍🩹
